    "It was the reason for his message of repentance and redemption.",
    "And it was the reason for his faith in God.",
    "Jonah looked at the city of Nineveh, his heart filled with love.",
    "He knew that God's mercy was enough, and he knew that he was blessed to be a part of it.",
    "And so, Jonah sat under his makeshift shelter, watching the city of Nineveh, his heart filled with gratitude and love."
